duties_responsibilities.duty: Follow established Standard Operating Procedures (SOP’s) to process orders including accurately picking, performing quality control checks, sorting, consolidating freight, building and wrapping pallets, packing, loading and preparing the orders for shipment.
Responsible for cross-training in multiple areas of the warehouse and/or participates in projects as assigned by your manager or other management team member.
Perform housekeeping and inventory control tasks, maintaining a clean work environment including complying with all Environmental Health and Safety requirements.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or GED preferred
